quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  8,49,"Jabke munafiqeen aur woh sab log jinke dilon ko rog laga hua hai, keh rahey thay ke in logon ko to inke deen ne khabat(delusion) mein mubtila kar rakkha hai, halanke agar koi Allah par bharosa karey to yakeenan Allah bada zabardast aur dana hai"
  8,50,"Kaash tum us halat ko dekh sakte jabke Farishte maktool kafiron ki roohein qabz kar rahey thay, woh unke chehron aur unke kulhon(backs) par zarb lagate jatey thay aur kehte jatey thay “ lo ab jalne ki saza bhugto"
  8,51,Yeh woh jaza hai jiska samaan tumhare apne haathon ne peshgi muhaiyya kar rakkha tha. Warna Allah to apne bandon par zulm karne wala nahin hai.”
  8,52,"Yeh maamla unke saath usi tarah pesh aaya jis tarah aale Firoun aur unse pehle ke dusre logon ke saath pesh aata raha hai, ke unhon ne Allah ki aayat ko maanne se inkar kiya aur Allah ne unke gunahon par unhein pakad liya. Allah quwwat rakhta ahi aur sakht saza dene wala hai"
  8,53,Yeh Allah ki is sunnat ke mutabiq hua ke woh kisi niyamat ko jo usne kisi qaum ko ata ki ho us waqt tak nahin badalta jab tak ke woh qaum khud apne tarz e amal ko nahin badal deti. Allah sab kuch sunne aur jaanne wala hai
  8,54,"Aale Firoun aur unse pehle ki qaumon ke saath jo kuch pesh aaya woh isi zaabtey ke mutabiq tha. Unhon ne apne Rubb ki aayat ko jhutlaya, tab humne unke gunahon ki padash mein unhein halaak kiya aur aale-Firoun ko garq kardiya, Yeh sab zalim log thay"
  8,55,Yaqeenan Allah ke nazdeek zameen par chalne wali makhlooq mein sabse badhtar woh log hain jinhon ne haqq ko maanne se inkar kardiya phir kisi tarah woh usey qabool karne par tayyar nahin hain
  8,56,(khusoosan) unmein se woh log jinke saath tu nay muahida (covenant) kiya phir woh har mauqe par usko todhte hain aur zara khuda ka khauf nahin karte
  8,57,Pas agar yeh log tumhein ladayi mein mil jayein to inki aisi khabar lo ke inke baad jo dusre log aisi rawish ikhtiyar karne waley hon unke hawaas bakhta (admonished) ho jayein. Tawakku hai ke badh-ahadon ke is anjaam se woh sabaq lenge
  8,58,"Aur agar kabhi kisi qaum se khayanat (treachery) ka andesha ho to uske muhaiday ko elaniya(publicly) uske aagey phenk do, yaqeenan Allah khayano (treacherous) ko pasand nahin karta"